{"tid":1564472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一間！你一陣會食既黃色餐廳！","createTime":"2019-09-12T19:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T05:32:35.000Z","uid":137371,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae9fcf9c13e3cb5b5cf386208e359f95d565170","tid":1564472,"uid":137371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"罷食呢 我就相信好多人都做緊喇 請繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動既呢段時間，遊客的確係少左，行街都舒服左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但同我地同一陣線既餐廳商店生意點都會受影響架。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地罷食既同時，我地更加要支持番同一陣線既商店。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對家既商店餐廳就攬住班黑警死全家啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望咁多位手足，講一講自己咩區，今日支持邊間餐廳。身體力行既同時，又可以提點下其他自己區既手足，成班手足聚埋一齊都食得爽d啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以用黃業bot: <a href=\"https://t.me/ybshopbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fybshopbot&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=1bbd67f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ybshopbot</a><br />\n<br />\nor <a href=\"https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restart-hk.com%2FShopList.html&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=69189a66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce99116e0b637ad4eaff3f5c3dcdb5d9a7ca1261","tid":1564472,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></s